                                課程簡介
                            

                                 
                            

                                 
                            

                                Introduction
                            





                                一、課程內容摘要：•	瞭解數位行銷、行動平臺、及O2O等精準行銷技巧•	能執行Facebook粉絲頁行銷企劃•	國內外網路個案研討二、本課程為2學分 (36小時)

《 課程簡介 -- English 》
                                As the digital marketing landscape continues to grow at a rapid pace, challenges and opportunities arise for new venture.The course is designed to lecture the Internet trend and development, also motivate students to practice precision marketing on Facebook. Relevant business cases are discussed in this course.











                                Material
                            

                                 
                            

                                上課教材
                            

                                 
                            





                                •	周世惠著，台灣臉書效應：Facebook行銷實戰，臺北：天下雜誌出版•	劉滄碩著，LINE@行動行銷─邁向百萬級店家，臺北：碁峰











